rows.label: qst701702_msg0001
rows.name:
The Bloody Lobsters?
What kind of nefarious business have
you got yourselves tangled up in?

rows.label: qst701702_msg0002
rows.name:
I can't say I'm intimately familiar, but
you can't help hearing things. They're
mostly famous for their brutality.

rows.label: qst701702_msg0003
rows.name:
I don't know why you're asking after
them, but some friendly advice: stop
right there. No good can come of it.

rows.label: qst701702_msg0004
rows.name:
You know what they say. "Don't put
your head on the block unless you're
ready for the axe". Best steer clear.
